REFERENCE           HOW_TO_PLAY_JKO
LANG_ENGLISH        "HOW TO PLAY JEDI KNIGHT: JEDI OUTCAST IN MD"
LANG_CZECH       "JAK HRAT JEDI KNIGHT: JEDI OUTCAST V MD"

REFERENCE           JKOHTP
LANG_ENGLISH        "1) You must own Jedi Knight: Jedi Outcast.\n 2) Download the Movie Duels JKO addon file from ModDB and install it into your MD folder.\n 3) Go into your JKO GameData > base folder and rename the 3 assets.pk3 files so they start with "0-".\n 4) Copy and paste the 3 renamed assets.pk3 files into your JKA base folder so it looks like the image below.\n\n You are now ready to start playing Jedi Outcast in MD."
LANG_CZECH       "1) Musite vlastnit Jedi Knight: Jedi Outcast.\n 2) Stahnete si Movie Duels JKO soubor rozsireni z ModDB a nainstalujte ho do Vasi MD slozky.\n 3) Jdete do Vaseho JKO Gamedata > base slozky a prejmenujte 3 assets.pk3 soubory, tak ze zacinaji s "0-".\n 4) Kopirujte a vlozte 3 prejmenovane assets.pk3 soubory do Vasi JKA base slozky, aby to vypadalo jako na obrazku dole.\n\n Ted uz jste pripraven zacit hra Jedi Outcast v MD."

