REFERENCE           DM_N_TFF
LANG_ENGLISH        "Naboo - Trade Federation Flagship"
LANG_CZECH       "Naboo - Vlajkova lod Obchodni Federace"

REFERENCE           DM_N_TFF_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Naboo - Trade Federation Flagship\nA massive, heavily-armed warship, designed for command and military operations. Its imposing design reflects the power and authority of the Trade Federation."
LANG_CZECH       "Naboo - Vlajkova lod Obchodni Federace\nMasivni, tezce ozbrojena valecna lod urcena pro veleni a vojenske operace. Jeji impozantni design odrazi moc a autoritu Obchodni Federace."

REFERENCE           DM_N_COT
LANG_ENGLISH        "Naboo - City Of Theed"
LANG_CZECH       "Naboo - Mesto Theed"

REFERENCE 	    DM_N_COT_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH 	 "Naboo - City Of Theed\nTheed is the capital city of Naboo, known for its stunning architecture, lush landscapes, and the iconic Theed Palace. It's a peaceful and culturally rich center of government and diplomacy."
LANG_CZECH       "Naboo - Mesto Theed\nTheed je hlavni mesto Naboo, zname svou uchvatnou architekturou, bujnou krajinou a ikonickym palacem Theed. Je to klidne a kulturne bohate centrum vlady a diplomacie."

REFERENCE           DM_N_OG
LANG_ENGLISH        "Naboo - Otoh Gunga"
LANG_CZECH       "#same"

REFERENCE           DM_N_OG_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Naboo - Otoh Gunga\nAn underwater city known for its bubble-like architecture and peaceful, aquatic environment. Otoh Gunga serves as the heart of Gungan culture and leadership."
LANG_CZECH       "Naboo - Otoh Gunga\nPodvodni mesto zname svou bublinovou architekturou a klidnym vodnim prostredim. Otoh Gunga je srdcem gunganske kultury a jejich vedeni."

REFERENCE           DM_T_MES
LANG_ENGLISH        "Tatooine - Mos Espa Spaceport"
LANG_CZECH       "Tatooine - Vesmirny pristav Mos Espa"

REFERENCE           DM_T_MES_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Tatooine - Mos Espa Spaceport\nA bustling trade hub on the desert planet Tatooine, known for its bustling market and podracing events. Mos Espa serves as a key point for travelers and traders in the Outer Rim."
LANG_CZECH       "Tatooine - Vesmirny pristav Mos Espa\nRusne obchodni centrum na poustni planete Tatooine, zname svym rusnym trzistem a zavody kluzaku. Mos Espa slouzi jako klicovy bod pro cestovatele a obchodniky ve Vnejsim okruhu."

REFERENCE           DM_N_TGC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Naboo - Theed Generator Complex"
LANG_CZECH       "Naboo - Generatorovy komplex mesta Theed"

REFERENCE           DM_N_TGC_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Naboo - Theed Generator Complex\nA vital power station on Naboo, the Theed Generator Complex provides energy to the capital city. Its advanced technology plays a key role in supporting the peaceful society of Naboo."
LANG_CZECH       "Naboo - Generatorovy komplex mesta Theed\nGeneratorovy komplex Theed, dulezita elektrarna na Naboo, dodava energii hlavnimu mestu. Jeho pokrocila technologie hraje klicovou roli v podpore mirove spolecnosti na Naboo."

REFERENCE           DM_N_QGF
LANG_ENGLISH        "Naboo - Qui-Gon's Funeral"
LANG_CZECH       "Naboo - Qui-Gonuv pohreb"

REFERENCE           DM_N_QGF_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Naboo - Qui-Gon's Funeral\nA solemn location where the funeral of Jedi Master Qui-Gon Jinn took place. The serene surroundings reflect the loss of a great leader and mentor."
LANG_CZECH       "Naboo - Qui-Gonuv pohreb\nVznesene misto, kde se konal pohreb mistra Jedi Qui-Gona Jinna. Klidne okoli odrazi ztratu velkeho vudce a mentora."

REFERENCE           DM_K_CF
LANG_ENGLISH        "Kamino - Cloning Facility"
LANG_CZECH       "Kamino - Klonovaci zarizeni"

REFERENCE           DM_K_CF_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Kamino - Cloning Facility\nAn advanced facility on the stormy world of Kamino, where the cloning process for the Grand Army of the Republic takes place. The facility is known for its towering architecture and endless rain."
LANG_CZECH       "Kamino - Klonovaci zarizeni\nPokrocile zarizeni na bourlivem svete Kamino, kde probiha klonovaci proces pro Velkou armadu Republiky. Zarizeni je zname svou impozantni architekturou a nekonecnym destem."

REFERENCE           DM_K_LP
LANG_ENGLISH        "Kamino - Landing Platform"
LANG_CZECH       "Kamino - Pristavaci plosina"

REFERENCE           DM_K_LP_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Kamino - Landing Platform\nA high-tech landing platform on Kamino, used for transporting visitors and supplies to and from the cloning facilities. It offers a stunning view of the planet's relentless storms."
LANG_CZECH       "Kamino - Pristavaci plosina\nHigh-tech pristavaci platforma na Kaminu, pouzivana k preprave navstevniku a zasob do a z klonovacich zarizeni. Nabizi uchvatny vyhled na neustavajici boure planety."

REFERENCE           DM_T_TC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Tatooine - Tusken Camp"
LANG_CZECH       "Tatooine - Tabor Tuskenu"

REFERENCE           DM_T_TC_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Tatooine - Tusken Camp\nA remote camp on the desert planet Tatooine, home to the nomadic Tusken Raiders. The harsh environment and primitive structures reflect the harsh life of the desert dwellers."
LANG_CZECH       "Tatooine - Tabor Tuskenu\nVzdaleny tabor na poustni planete Tatooine, domove kocovnych Tuskenu. Drsne prostredi a primitivni stavby odrazeji tvrdy zivot obyvatel pouste."

REFERENCE           DM_G_PA
LANG_ENGLISH        "Geonosis - Petranaki Arena"
LANG_CZECH       "Geonosis - Arena Petranaki"

REFERENCE           DM_G_PA_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Geonosis - Petranaki Arena\nAn ancient arena on Geonosis where deadly battles take place. The Petranaki Arena is infamous for its brutal gladiatorial combat, particularly during the Battle of Geonosis."
LANG_CZECH       "Geonosis - Arena Petranaki\nStarobyla arena na Geonosis, kde se odehravaji smrtici bitvy. Arena Petranaki je nechvalne znama svymi brutalnimi gladiatorskymi souboji, zejmena behem Bitvy o Geonosis."

REFERENCE           DM_G_B
LANG_ENGLISH        "Geonosis - Battlefield"
LANG_CZECH       "Geonosis - Bitevni pole"

REFERENCE           DM_G_B_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Geonosis - Battlefield\nThe war-torn landscape of Geonosis, site of the first major battle of the Clone Wars. The battlefield is littered with wreckage and evidence of the brutal conflict between the Separatists and the Republic."
LANG_CZECH       "Geonosis - Bitevni pole\nValkou zpustosena krajina Geonosis, misto prvni velke bitvy Klonovych valek. Bojiste je poseto troskami a stopami brutalniho konfliktu mezi Separatisty a Republikou."

REFERENCE           DM_G_DSH
LANG_ENGLISH        "Geonosis - Dooku's Secret Hangar"
LANG_CZECH       "Geonosis - Skryty hangar Hrabete Dooku"

REFERENCE           DM_G_DSH_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Geonosis - Dooku's Secret Hangar\nA hidden hangar on Geonosis, used by Count Dooku to secretly store ships and equipment. Its concealed nature reflects the secrecy surrounding Dooku's plans for the galaxy."
LANG_CZECH       "Geonosis - Skryty hangar Hrabete Dooku\nSkryty hangar na Geonosis, ktery hrabe Dooku pouzival k tajnemu skladovani lodi a vybaveni. Jeho skryta povaha odrazi utajeni, ktere obklopuje Dookuovy plany pro galaxii."

REFERENCE           DM_C_TIH
LANG_ENGLISH        "Coruscant - The Invisible Hand"
LANG_CZECH       "#same"

REFERENCE           DM_C_TIH_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Coruscant - The Invisible Hand\nA powerful flagship of the Confederacy, The Invisible Hand serves as Count Dooku's command ship. Its intimidating design and size reflect the might of the Separatist Alliance."
LANG_CZECH       "Coruscant - The Invisible Hand\nMocna vlajkova lod Konfederace, The Invisible Hand, slouzi jako velitelska lod hrabete Dooku. Jeji impozantni design a velikost odrazeji moc Separatisticke Aliance."

REFERENCE           DM_U_PC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Utapau - Pau City"
LANG_CZECH       "Utapau - Mesto Pau"

REFERENCE           DM_U_PC_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Utapau - Pau City\nA sprawling city built into the deep sinkholes of Utapau, known for its towering spires and unique, cliffside architecture. Pau City is home to the planet's native species, the Pau'ans."
LANG_CZECH       "Utapau - Mesto Pau\nRozlehle mesto postavene v hlubokych propadlinach Utapau, zname svymi vysokymi vezemi a jedinecnou architekturou na uboci utesu. Mesto Pau je domovem puvodnich obyvatel planety, Pau'anu."

REFERENCE           DM_U_SLP
LANG_ENGLISH        "Utapau - Secret Landing Platform"
LANG_CZECH       "Utapau - Skryta pristavaci plosina"

REFERENCE           DM_U_SLP_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Utapau - Secret Landing Platform\nA hidden landing platform located deep within the sinkholes of Utapau. It serves as a discreet landing point for important visitors, away from the city's main entrances."
LANG_CZECH       "Utapau - Skryta pristavaci plosina\nSkryta pristavaci plosina umistena hluboko v propadlinach Utapau. Slouzi jako diskretni pristavaci misto pro dulezite navstevniky, daleko od hlavnich vchodu do mesta."

REFERENCE           DM_M_B
LANG_ENGLISH        "Mygeeto - Bridge"
LANG_CZECH       "Mygeeto - Most"

REFERENCE           DM_M_B_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Mygeeto - Bridge\nA strategically important bridge on the icy world of Mygeeto, linking two vast sections of the planet's frozen landscape. It was a key location during the Clone Wars, with fierce battles fought to control it."
LANG_CZECH       "Mygeeto - Most\nStrategicky dulezity most na ledovem svete Mygeeto, spojujici dve rozsahle casti zamrzle krajiny planety. Behem Klonovych valek byl klicovym mistem, o jehoz kontrolu se vedly zurive bitvy."

REFERENCE           DM_C_C
LANG_ENGLISH        "Coruscant - City"
LANG_CZECH       "Coruscant - Mesto"

REFERENCE           DM_C_C_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Coruscant - City\nThe vast, urban expanse of Coruscant, the galactic capital, is home to countless levels of cityscape, from towering skyscrapers to sprawling districts. It is the heart of political power in the galaxy."
LANG_CZECH       "Coruscant - Mesto\nRozlehla mestska aglomerace Coruscantu, galaktickeho hlavniho mesta, je domovem nescetnych urovni mestske krajiny, od tycicich se mrakodrapu po rozlehle ctvrti. Je to srdce politicke moci v galaxii."

REFERENCE           DM_C_PA
LANG_ENGLISH        "Coruscant - Padme's Apartment"
LANG_CZECH       "Coruscant - Apartman Padme Amidaly"

REFERENCE           DM_C_PA_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Coruscant - Padme's Apartment\nA luxurious residence in the heart of Coruscant, Padme Amidala's apartment offers stunning views of the cityscape. It serves as a quiet retreat from the chaos of galactic politics."
LANG_CZECH       "Coruscant - Apartman Padme Amidaly\nLuxusni rezidence v srdci Coruscantu, byt Padme Amidaly, nabizi uchvatny vyhled na panorama mesta. Slouzi jako klidne utociste pred chaosem galakticke politiky."

REFERENCE           DM_C_PO
LANG_ENGLISH        "Coruscant - Palpatine's Office"
LANG_CZECH       "Coruscant - Palpatinova kancelar"

REFERENCE           DM_C_PO_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Coruscant - Palpatine's Office\nLocated within the Senate building, Palpatine's office is a place of both political strategy and manipulation. The office offers a commanding view of Coruscant and reflects the Chancellor's growing influence."
LANG_CZECH       "Coruscant - Palpatinova kancelar\nKancelar Palpatina, ktera se nachazi v budove Senatu, je mistem politickych strategii i manipulace. Z kancelare je nadherny vyhled na Coruscant a odrazi rostouci vliv Kanclere."

REFERENCE           DM_C_JTO
LANG_ENGLISH        "Coruscant - Jedi Temple Outside"
LANG_CZECH       "Coruscant - Chram Jediu (venku)"

REFERENCE           DM_C_JTO_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Coruscant - Jedi Temple Outside\nThe grand exterior of the Jedi Temple, located at the heart of Coruscant. Its towering spires and vast courtyards reflect the temple's significance as the center of Jedi teachings and wisdom."
LANG_CZECH       "Coruscant - Chram Jediu (venku)\nVelkolepy exterier chramu Jediu, ktery se nachazi v samem srdci Coruscantu. Jeho tycici se veze a rozlehla nadvori odrazeji vyznam chramu jako centra uceni a moudrosti Jediu."

REFERENCE           DM_C_JT
LANG_ENGLISH        "Coruscant - Jedi Temple"
LANG_CZECH       "Coruscant - Chram Jediu"

REFERENCE           DM_C_JT_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Coruscant - Jedi Temple\nThe sacred home of the Jedi Order on Coruscant, this temple is the heart of Jedi training and philosophy. It houses vast libraries and is a symbol of peace and knowledge across the galaxy."
LANG_CZECH       "Coruscant - Chram Jediu\nTento chram, posvatne sidlo radu Jediu na Coruscantu, je centrem vycviku a filozofie Jediu. Nachazeji se v nem rozsahle knihovny a je symbolem miru a vedeni v cele galaxii."

REFERENCE           DM_JT_TR
LANG_ENGLISH        "Jedi Temple - Training Room"
LANG_CZECH       "Chram Jediu - Vycvikova mistnost"

REFERENCE           DM_JT_TR_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Jedi Temple - Training Room\nA dedicated space within the Jedi Temple for young Jedi to hone their skills. The training room features combat droids and holographic simulations for various forms of combat and discipline."
LANG_CZECH       "Chram Jediu - Vycvikova mistnost\nSpecialni prostor v chramu Jediu, kde mladi Jediove zdokonaluji sve dovednosti. Treninkova mistnost je vybavena bojovymi droidy a holografickymi simulacemi ruznych forem boje a discipliny."

REFERENCE           DM_JT_LA
LANG_ENGLISH        "Jedi Temple - Ruins"
LANG_CZECH       "Chram Jediu - Ruiny"

REFERENCE           DM_JT_LA_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Jedi Temple - Ruins\nThe remnants of the once majestic Jedi Temple, now a site of devastation and loss. The ruins stand as a somber reminder of the fall of the Jedi Order and the rise of the Empire."
LANG_CZECH       "Chram Jediu - Ruiny\nZbytky kdysi majestatniho chramu Jediu, dnes misto zkazy a ztraty. Ruiny jsou ponurym pripomenutim padu radu Jediu a vzestupu Imperia."

REFERENCE           DM_JT_LP
LANG_ENGLISH        "Jedi Temple - Landing Platform"
LANG_CZECH       "Chram Jediu - Pristavaci plosina"

REFERENCE           DM_JT_LP_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Jedi Temple - Landing Platform\nA landing platform situated atop the Jedi Temple, used for docking ships and receiving important visitors. It offers a breathtaking view of Coruscant's vast cityscape."
LANG_CZECH       "Chram Jediu - Pristavaci plosina\nPristavaci plosina umistena na vrcholu chramu Jediu, slouzici k pristavani lodi a prijimani dulezitych navstevniku. Nabizi uchvatny vyhled na rozlehlou mestskou krajinu Coruscantu."

REFERENCE           DM_C_SC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Coruscant - Senate Complex"
LANG_CZECH       "Coruscant - Senatni komplex"

REFERENCE           DM_C_SC_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Coruscant - Senate Complex\nThe massive and intricate Senate Complex on Coruscant, where galactic politics unfold. This sprawling structure houses the Galactic Senate and serves as the center of legislative power in the Republic."
LANG_CZECH       "Coruscant - Senatni komplex\nObrovsky a slozity komplex Senatu na Coruscantu, kde se odehrava galakticka politika. Tato rozlehla budova je sidlem Galaktickeho Senatu a slouzi jako centrum zakonodarne moci Republiky."

REFERENCE           DM_M_MF
LANG_ENGLISH        "Mustafar - Mining Facility"
LANG_CZECH       "Mustafar - Tezebni zarizeni"

REFERENCE           DM_M_MF_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Mustafar - Mining Facility\nA harsh industrial complex on the volcanic planet Mustafar, where valuable resources are extracted under extreme conditions. The facility is a key location for the Separatists during the Clone Wars."
LANG_CZECH       "Mustafar - Tezebni zarizeni\nDrsny prumyslovy komplex na vulkanicke planete Mustafar, kde se za extremnich podminek tezi cenne suroviny. Zarizeni je klicovym mistem pro Separatisty behem Klonovych valek."

REFERENCE           DM_M_MFD
LANG_ENGLISH        "Mustafar - Mining Facility Duel"
LANG_CZECH       "Mustafar - Duel v tezebnim zarizeni"

REFERENCE           DM_M_MFD_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Mustafar - Mining Facility Duel\nA fiery and treacherous location within the mining facility on Mustafar, where Obi-Wan Kenobi and Anakin Skywalker engage in their final, fateful duel. The surroundings are dominated by molten lava and intense heat."
LANG_CZECH       "Mustafar - Duel v tezebnim zarizeni\nOhnive a zradne misto v tezebnim zarizeni na Mustafaru, kde Obi-Wan Kenobi a Anakin Skywalker svadeji svuj posledni, osudovy souboj. Okoli ovlada roztavena lava a intenzivni zar."

REFERENCE           DM_M_SPD
LANG_ENGLISH        "Mandalore - Sundari Palace (Day)"
LANG_CZECH       "Mandalore - Palac Sundari (Den)"

REFERENCE           DM_M_SPD_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Mandalore - Sundari Palace (Day)\nThe grand palace of Mandalore, located in the city of Sundari. During the day, the palace shines under the bright sun, reflecting the regal power and history of Mandalore's leadership."
LANG_CZECH       "Mandalore - Palac Sundari (Den)\nVelkolepy palac Mandalore, ktery se nachazi ve meste Sundari. Behem dne palac zari pod jasnym sluncem a odrazi kralovskou moc a historii mandalorianskeho vedeni."

REFERENCE           DM_M_SPN
LANG_ENGLISH        "Mandalore - Sundari Palace (Night)"
LANG_CZECH       "Mandalore - Palac Sundari (Noc)"

REFERENCE           DM_M_SPN_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Mandalore - Sundari Palace (Night)\nThe Sundari Palace at night, illuminated by the soft glow of lights against the dark Mandalorian sky. The palace exudes a calm yet imposing presence, reflecting the strength and resilience of Mandalore's rulers."
LANG_CZECH       "Mandalore - Palac Sundari (Noc)\nPalac Sundari v noci, osvetleny jemnym svitem svetel proti temne mandalorianske obloze. Palac vyzaruje klidnou, ale impozantni pritomnost, odrazejici silu a odolnost mandalorianskych vladcu."

REFERENCE           DM_RS_TR
LANG_ENGLISH        "Rogue Shadow - Training Room"
LANG_CZECH       "Rogue Shadow - Vycvikova mistnost"

REFERENCE           DM_RS_TR_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Rogue Shadow - Training Room\nA training facility aboard the Rogue Shadow, used to hone combat skills and prepare for dangerous missions. The room is equipped with advanced simulations and droid combatants."
LANG_CZECH       "Rogue Shadow - Vycvikova mistnost\nVycvikove zarizeni na palube lodi Rogue Shadow, ktere slouzi k zdokonalovani bojovych dovednosti a priprave na nebezpecne mise. Mistnost je vybavena pokrocilymi simulatory a bojovymi droidy."

REFERENCE           DM_DS_TFU
LANG_ENGLISH        "Death Star - The Force Unleashed"
LANG_CZECH       "Hvezda Smrti - The Force Unleashed"

REFERENCE           DM_DS_TFU_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Death Star - The Force Unleashed\nA chamber on the Death Star where intense battles unfold. The location is tied to the secret training and experiments of the Sith, where dark power and destruction are unleashed."
LANG_CZECH       "Hvezda Smrti - The Force Unleashed\nKomnata na Hvezde smrti, kde se odehravaji intenzivni bitvy. Toto misto je spojeno s tajnym vycvikem a experimenty Sithu, kde se uvolnuje temna sila a niceni."

REFERENCE           DM_S_WBW
LANG_ENGLISH        "Space - World Between Worlds"
LANG_CZECH       "Vesmir - Svet mezi svety"

REFERENCE           DM_S_WBW_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Space - World Between Worlds\nA mystical, dimension-bending space that exists outside the known galaxy. The World Between Worlds serves as a portal to alternate realities and key moments in history, a place of great mystery and danger."
LANG_CZECH       "Vesmir - Svet mezi svety\nMysticky prostor, ktery prekracuje hranice dimenzi a existuje mimo znamou galaxii. Svet mezi svety slouzi jako brana do alternativnich realit a klicovych momentu historie. Je to misto plne tajemstvi a nebezpeci."

REFERENCE           DM_J_HC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Jedha - Holy City"
LANG_CZECH       "Jedha - Posvatne mesto"

REFERENCE           DM_J_HC_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Jedha - Holy City\nThe ancient city of Jedha, a sacred place for those who follow the Force. It is home to ancient temples and ruins, a center of pilgrimage for Force users before it was destroyed during the Galactic Empire's conquest."
LANG_CZECH       "Jedha - Posvatne mesto\nStarobyle mesto Jedha, posvatne misto pro ty, kteri nasleduji Silu. Je domovem starobylych chramu a ruin, poutnim mistem pro uzivatele Sily, predtim, nez bylo zniceno behem dobyvani Galaktickym Imperiem."

REFERENCE           DM_M_VC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Mustafar - Vader's Castle"
LANG_CZECH       "Mustafar - Vaderova pevnost"

REFERENCE           DM_M_VC_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Mustafar - Vader's Castle\nA towering fortress on the volcanic world of Mustafar, built by Darth Vader to symbolize his power and to meditate in isolation. The castle is a haunting place of dark energy and intense heat."
LANG_CZECH       "Mustafar - Vaderova pevnost\nVysoka pevnost na vulkanickem svete Mustafar, postavena Darth Vaderem jako symbol jeho moci a misto pro meditaci v izolaci. Hrad je strasidelnym mistem temne energie a intenzivniho tepla."

REFERENCE           DM_S_ISC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Scarif - Imperial Security Complex"
LANG_CZECH       "Scarif - Imperialni bezpecnostni komplex"

REFERENCE           DM_S_ISC_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Scarif - Imperial Security Complex\nA heavily fortified complex on Scarif, housing the Empire's top secret operations. The facility's remote location and high security make it a key strategic asset for the Empire."
LANG_CZECH       "Scarif - Imperialni bezpecnostni komplex\nSilne opevneny komplex na Scarifu, kde se odehravaji prisne tajne operace Imperia. Diky sve odlehle poloze a vysoke urovni zabezpeceni je tento komplex klicovym strategickym aktivem Imperia."

REFERENCE           DM_SC_PH
LANG_ENGLISH        "Star Cruiser - Profundity Hallway"
LANG_CZECH       "Hvezdny kriznik - Chodba na Profundity"

REFERENCE           DM_SC_PH_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Star Cruiser - Profundity Hallway\nA long, sleek hallway aboard the Profundity, a Rebel Alliance star cruiser. The hallway connects key areas of the ship, featuring utilitarian design and the constant hum of activity during fleet operations."
LANG_CZECH       "Hvezdny kriznik - Chodba na Profundity\nDlouha, elegantni chodba na palube Profundity, hvezdneho krizniku Povstalecke Aliance. Chodba spojuje klicove casti lodi, vyznacuje se utilitarnim designem a neustalym ruchem behem operaci flotily."

REFERENCE           DM_T_RBR
LANG_ENGLISH        "Tantive IV - Rebel Blockade Runner"
LANG_CZECH       "Tantive IV - Povstalecky blokadni bezec"

REFERENCE           DM_T_RBR_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Tantive IV - Rebel Blockade Runner\nThe Tantive IV, a Rebel blockade runner, is a fast and agile ship used for stealth and escape. The ship's design combines speed with practicality, serving as a vital tool for the Rebel Alliance."
LANG_CZECH       "Tantive IV - Povstalecky blokadni bezec\nTantive IV, blokadni lod Rebelu, je rychla a obratna lod pouzivana k utajeni a uniku. Konstrukce lodi kombinuje rychlost s prakticnosti a slouzi jako nezbytny nastroj pro Povstaleckou Alianci."

REFERENCE           DM_T_LHO
LANG_ENGLISH        "Tatooine - Lars Homestead Outside"
LANG_CZECH       "Tatooine - Larsova farma (Venku)"

REFERENCE           DM_T_LHO_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Tatooine - Lars Homestead Outside\nThe quiet, moisture farm of the Lars family on Tatooine, surrounded by harsh desert. This humble home serves as a refuge for Luke Skywalker, and its simple structure reflects the desert life of its inhabitants."
LANG_CZECH       "Tatooine - Larsova farma (Venku)\nTicha, vlhka farma rodiny Larsu na Tatooine, obklopena drsnou pousti. Tento skromny domov slouzi jako utociste pro Luka Skywalkera a jeho jednoducha struktura odrazi poustni zivot jeho obyvatel."

REFERENCE           DM_T_TS
LANG_ENGLISH        "Tatooine - Twin Suns"
LANG_CZECH       "Tatooine - Dve slunce"

REFERENCE           DM_T_TS_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Tatooine - Twin Suns\nSet under the starry sky of Tatooine at night, this desert landscape is marked by sweeping sands. The location is iconic for its quiet, tense atmosphere, where the final confrontation between Maul and Obi-Wan took place."
LANG_CZECH       "Tatooine - Dve slunce\nTato poustni krajina, zasazena pod nocni hvezdnou oblohou Tatooine, je charakteristicka rozsahlymi pisecnymi dunami. Misto je zname svou tichou, napjatou atmosferou, kde doslo k finalnimu stretu mezi Maulem a Obi-Wanem."

REFERENCE           DM_T_O
LANG_ENGLISH        "Tatooine - Outpost"
LANG_CZECH       "Tatooine - Predsunuta hlidka"

REFERENCE           DM_T_O_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Tatooine - Outpost\nA remote outpost in the deserts of Tatooine, serving as a waypoint for travelers and traders. The outpost is a lifeline in the harsh desert, with minimal resources and constant danger."
LANG_CZECH       "Tatooine - Predsunuta hlidka\nVzdalena zakladna v pousti Tatooine, slouzici jako zastavka pro cestovatele a obchodniky. Zakladna je zachrannym lanem v drsne pousti, kde jsou minimalni zdroje a neustale nebezpeci."

REFERENCE           DM_TE_MC
LANG_ENGLISH        "The Executor - Vader's Flagship"
LANG_CZECH       "The Executor - Vaderova vlajkova lod"

REFERENCE           DM_TE_MC_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "The Executor - Vader's Flagship\nThe Executor is Darth Vader's massive flagship, a symbol of Imperial might. With its imposing size and firepower, it serves as a command center for the fleet, carrying out the will of the Empire."
LANG_CZECH       "The Executor - Vaderova vlajkova lod\nExecutor je mohutna vlajkova lod Dartha Vadera, symbol imperialni moci. Diky sve impozantni velikosti a palebne sile slouzi jako velitelske centrum flotily a plni vuli Imperia."

REFERENCE           DM_DS_SS
LANG_ENGLISH        "Death Star - Space Station"
LANG_CZECH       "Hvezda Smrti - Vesmirna stanice"

REFERENCE           DM_DS_SS_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Death Star - Space Station\nA colossal space station and superweapon, the Death Star is capable of destroying entire planets. It is a symbol of the Empire's terror, with its cold, mechanical design and overwhelming power."
LANG_CZECH       "Hvezda Smrti - Vesmirna stanice\nObrovska vesmirna stanice a superzbran, Hvezda Smrti, je schopna znicit cele planety. Je symbolem teroru Imperia, s chladnym, mechanickym designem a ohromujici silou."

REFERENCE           DM_Y_TGT
LANG_ENGLISH        "Yavin IV - The Great Temple"
LANG_CZECH       "Yavin IV - Velky chram"

REFERENCE           DM_Y_TGT_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Yavin IV - The Great Temple\nAn ancient, jungle-covered temple on Yavin IV, once home to the massassi warriors. It became the Rebel Alliance's base of operations during the Battle of Yavin, where the Death Star was destroyed."
LANG_CZECH       "Yavin IV - Velky chram\nStarobyly chram pokryty dzungli na Yavinu IV, kdysi domov valecniku Massassi. Behem Bitvy o Yavin, kdy byla znicena Hvezda Smrti, se stal operacni zakladnou Povstalecke Aliance."

REFERENCE           DM_Y_CH
LANG_ENGLISH        "Yavin IV - Ceremonial Hall"
LANG_CZECH       "Yavin IV - Obradni mistnost"

REFERENCE           DM_Y_CH_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Yavin IV - Ceremonial Hall\nA large, open hall within the Great Temple on Yavin IV, where the Rebel Alliance holds ceremonies and meetings. The hall is a place of reflection and celebration, most famously for the heroes of the Battle of Yavin."
LANG_CZECH       "Yavin IV - Obradni mistnost\nObrovska otevrena hala v ramci Velkeho chramu na Yavinu IV, kde Povstalecka Aliance porada ceremonie a schuze. Hala je mistem reflexe a oslav. Nejznamejsimi jsou oslavy hrdinu Bitvy o Yavin."

REFERENCE           DM_H_EB
LANG_ENGLISH        "Hoth - Echo Base"
LANG_CZECH       "Hoth - Zakladna Echo"

REFERENCE           DM_H_EB_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Hoth - Echo Base\nA secret Rebel base located on the icy planet of Hoth. Echo Base is a fortress carved into the planet's frozen caverns, serving as the staging ground for the Rebel Alliance's fight against the Empire."
LANG_CZECH       "Hoth - Zakladna Echo\nTajna zakladna Povstalcu umistena na ledove planete Hoth. Echo Base je pevnost vytesana do zamrzlych jeskyni planety, ktera slouzi jako zakladna pro boj Povstalecke Aliance proti Imperiu."

REFERENCE           DM_B_CC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Bespin - Cloud City"
LANG_CZECH       "Bespin - Oblacne mesto"

REFERENCE           DM_B_CC_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Bespin - Cloud City\nA floating city in the skies of Bespin, Cloud City is a mining colony that specializes in tibanna gas extraction. Known for its stunning views and industrial design, it serves as a hub for commerce and intrigue."
LANG_CZECH       "Bespin - Oblacne mesto\nOblacne mesto, vznasejici se mesto na obloze Bespinu, je tezebni kolonie specializujici se na tezbu tibannskeho plynu. Je zname svymi uchvatnymi vyhledy a prumyslovym designem a slouzi jako centrum obchodu a intrik."

REFERENCE           DM_B_CFC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Bespin - Carbon Freezing Chamber"
LANG_CZECH       "Bespin - Komora pro mrazeni karbonitu"

REFERENCE           DM_B_CFC_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Bespin - Carbon Freezing Chamber\nA cold, industrial chamber located within Cloud City, used for the freezing of subjects in carbonite. The chamber is infamous for the capture of Han Solo by Darth Vader."
LANG_CZECH       "Bespin - Komora pro mrazeni karbonitu\nChladna prumyslova komora umistena v Oblacnem meste, ktera slouzi k zmrazovani subjektu v karbonitu. Komora je znama diky zajeti Hana Sola Darth Vaderem."

REFERENCE           DM_T_GPOC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Tatooine - Great Pit of Carkoon"
LANG_CZECH       "Tatooine - Velka jama Carkoona"

REFERENCE           DM_T_GPOC_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Tatooine - Great Pit of Carkoon\nA vast, deadly pit in the desert of Tatooine, home to the fearsome Sarlacc. It is the site where Jabba the Hutt imprisons his enemies, and serves as the backdrop for a daring escape by Han Solo and his friends."
LANG_CZECH       "Tatooine - Velka jama Carkoona\nObrovska, smrtici jama v pousti Tatooine, domov strasliveho Sarlacca. Je to misto, kde Jabba Hutt vezni sve nepratele, a slouzi jako kulisa pro odvazny utek Hana Sola a jeho pratel."

REFERENCE           DM_T_JPD
LANG_ENGLISH        "Tatooine - Jabba's Palace (Day)"
LANG_CZECH       "Tatooine - Jabbuv palac (Den)"

REFERENCE           DM_T_JPD_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Tatooine - Jabba's Palace (Day)\nThe imposing palace of Jabba the Hutt, located in the deserts of Tatooine. By day, the palace is a fortress filled with intrigue, crime, and dangerous creatures under the control of the infamous gangster."
LANG_CZECH       "Tatooine - Jabbuv palac (Den)\nImpozantni palac Jabby Hutta, ktery se nachazi v poustich Tatooine. Ve dne je palac pevnosti plnou intrik, zlocinu a nebezpecnych tvoru pod kontrolou nechvalne znameho gangstera."

REFERENCE           DM_T_JPN
LANG_ENGLISH        "Tatooine - Jabba's Palace (Night)"
LANG_CZECH       "Tatooine - Jabbuv palac (Noc)"

REFERENCE           DM_T_JPN_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Tatooine - Jabba's Palace (Night)\nAt night, Jabba's Palace becomes a darker, more mysterious place, with shadowy figures moving through its halls. The desert heat cools, but the palace remains a place of power and treachery."
LANG_CZECH       "Tatooine - Jabbuv palac (Noc)\nV noci se Jabbuv palac stava temnejsim a tajemnejsim mistem, kde se po chodbach pohybuji stinove postavy. Poustni vedro ochlazuje, ale palac zustava mistem moci a zrady."

REFERENCE           DM_DS_ETR
LANG_ENGLISH        "Death Star II - Emperor's Throne Room"
LANG_CZECH       "Hvezda Smrti II - Cisaruv trunni sal"

REFERENCE           DM_DS_ETR_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Death Star II - Emperor's Throne Room\nA grand, ominous chamber located on the second Death Star, where Emperor Palpatine sits on his throne, watching over the galaxy's fate. The room is a symbol of the Empire's control and the Emperor's dark influence."
LANG_CZECH       "Hvezda Smrti II - Cisaruv trunni sal\nVelkolepa, zlovestna komnata nachazejici se na druhe Hvezde smrti, kde Cisar Palpatine sedi na svem trunu a dohlizi na osud galaxie. Tato mistnost je symbolem nadvlady Imperia a temneho vlivu Cisare."

REFERENCE           DM_J_T
LANG_ENGLISH        "Jakku - Tuanul"
LANG_CZECH       "#same"

REFERENCE           DM_J_T_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Jakku - Tuanul\nTuanul is a remote settlement on the desert planet Jakku, where scavengers and travelers make their home. The settlement is a harsh, barren place, but it plays a key role in the events leading to the rise of the Resistance."
LANG_CZECH       "Jakku - Tuanul\nTuanul je odlehla osada na poustni planete Jakku, kde ziji sberaci a cestovatele. Osada je drsnym a neurodnym mistem, ale hraje klicovou roli v udalostech, ktere vedou ke vzniku Odboje."

REFERENCE           DM_E_BF
LANG_ENGLISH        "Eravana - Bulk Freighter"
LANG_CZECH       "Eravana - Velka nakladni lod"

REFERENCE           DM_E_BF_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Eravana - Bulk Freighter\nThe Eravana is a large, aging bulk freighter that travels the galaxy, often carrying cargo and passengers through dangerous sectors. Its worn-down design and cramped interior reflect its history as a smuggler's vessel."
LANG_CZECH       "Eravana - Velka nakladni lod\nEravana je velka, starnouci nakladni lod, ktera cestuje po galaxii a casto prepravuje naklad a pasazery pres nebezpecne sektory. Jeji opotrebovany design a stisneny interier odrazeji jeji historii jako paseracke lodi."

REFERENCE           DM_SB_C
LANG_ENGLISH        "Starkiller Base - Complex"
LANG_CZECH       "Zakladna Hvezdovrah - Komplex"

REFERENCE           DM_SB_C_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Starkiller Base - Complex\nThe Starkiller Base complex is a massive military installation built into the heart of a planet. It is designed for strategic operations and housing the weapon capable of destroying entire star systems."
LANG_CZECH       "Zakladna Hvezdovrah - Komplex\nKomplex Zakladny Hvezdovrah je obrovska vojenska zakladna vybudovana v jadru planety. Je urcena pro strategicke operace a slouzi jako uloziste zbrane schopne znicit cele hvezdne systemy."

REFERENCE           DM_SB_F
LANG_ENGLISH        "Starkiller Base - Forest"
LANG_CZECH       "Zakladna Hvezdovrah - Les"

REFERENCE           DM_SB_F_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Starkiller Base - Forest\nA lush, dark forest located on Starkiller Base, this forest stands in stark contrast to the planet's destructive potential. It serves as the backdrop for the final confrontation between the Resistance and the First Order."
LANG_CZECH       "Zakladna Hvezdovrah - Les\nTento bujny, temny les se nachazi na Zakladne Hvezdovrah a je v ostrem kontrastu s destruktivnim potencialem planety. Slouzi jako kulisa pro finalni stretnuti mezi Odbojem a Prvnim Radem."

REFERENCE           DM_TS_STR
LANG_ENGLISH        "The Supremacy - Snoke's Throne Room"
LANG_CZECH       "The Supremacy - Snokeuv trunni sal"

REFERENCE           DM_TS_STR_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "The Supremacy - Snoke's Throne Room\nAn imposing throne room aboard the Supremacy, Supreme Leader Snoke's flagship. The room is a symbol of his power and authority, with a view of the galaxy that reflects his control over it."
LANG_CZECH       "The Supremacy - Snokeuv trunni sal\nImpozantni trunni sal na palube Supremacy, vlajkove lodi Nejvyssiho vudce Snokea. Tato mistnost je symbolem jeho moci a autority a nabizi vyhled na galaxii, ktery odrazi jeho kontrolu nad ni."

REFERENCE           DM_C_RO
LANG_ENGLISH        "Crait - Resistance Outpost"
LANG_CZECH       "Crait - Zakladna Odboje"

REFERENCE           DM_C_RO_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Crait - Resistance Outpost\nA secret Resistance outpost on the mineral-rich planet Crait, known for its stark white surface and red dust. The outpost served as a last stand for the Resistance against the overwhelming forces of the First Order."
LANG_CZECH       "Crait - Zakladna Odboje\nTajna zakladna Odboje na planete Crait, ktera je bohata na nerostne suroviny a znama svym snehove bilym povrchem a cervenym prachem. Tato zakladna slouzila jako posledni basta Odboje proti prevaze sil Prvniho Radu."

REFERENCE           DM_E_SC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Exegol - Sith Citadel"
LANG_CZECH       "Exegol - Sithska citadela"

REFERENCE           DM_E_SC_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Exegol - Sith Citadel\nA dark and foreboding citadel located on the hidden world of Exegol. The Sith Citadel serves as the base of operations for the Sith Eternal, where dark rituals and plans for galactic domination are carried out in secrecy."
LANG_CZECH       "Exegol - Sithska citadela\nTemna a zlovestna pevnost nachazejici se ve skrytem svete Exegol. Pevnost Sithu slouzi jako operacni zakladna pro kult "Vecny Sith", kde se v tajnosti provadeji temne ritualy a plany na ovladnuti galaxie."

REFERENCE           DM_C_CA
LANG_ENGLISH        "Corvus - Calodan"
LANG_CZECH       "#same"

REFERENCE           DM_C_CA_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Corvus - Calodan\nA desolate settlement on the planet Corvus. Once a thriving town, it now serves as the base of operations for Morgan Elsbeth, where dark dealings and dangerous confrontations unfold."
LANG_CZECH       "Corvus - Calodan\nOpustena osada na planete Corvus. Kdysi prosperujici mesto, dnes slouzi jako zakladna pro Morgana Elsbeth, kde se odehravaji temne obchody a nebezpecne konfrontace."

REFERENCE           DM_JT_D
LANG_ENGLISH        "Jedi Temple - Dojo"
LANG_CZECH       "Chram Jediu - Telocvicna"

REFERENCE           DM_JT_D_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Jedi Temple - Dojo\nA dedicated training chamber within the Jedi Temple on Coruscant. The Dojo is where Jedi refine their lightsaber skills and strengthen their connection to the Force."
LANG_CZECH       "Chram Jediu - Dojo\nSpecialni treninkova komora v chramu Jediu na Coruscantu. V Dojo Jediove zdokonaluji sve dovednosti se svetelnym mecem a posiluji sve spojeni se Silou."

REFERENCE           DM_K_F
LANG_ENGLISH        "Khofar - Forest"
LANG_CZECH       "Khofar - Les"

REFERENCE           DM_K_F_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Khofar - Forest\nA dense and humid forest world, Khofar is marked by towering trees and hidden dangers. Its wild terrain conceals secrets that draw both Jedi and those who hunt them."
LANG_CZECH       "Khofar - Les\nKhofar je husty a vlhky lesni svet, ktery se vyznacuje vysokymi stromy a skrytymi nebezpecimi. Jeho divoka krajina skryva tajemstvi, ktera pritahuji jak Jedie, tak ty, kteri je lovi."

REFERENCE           DM_T_LHD
LANG_ENGLISH        "Tatooine - Lars Homestead (Day)"
LANG_CZECH       "Tatooine - Larsova farma (Den)"

REFERENCE           DM_T_LHD_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Tatooine - Lars Homestead (Day)\nThe quiet, moisture farm of the Lars family on Tatooine, surrounded by harsh desert. This humble home serves as a refuge for Luke Skywalker, and its simple structure reflects the desert life of its inhabitants."
LANG_CZECH       "Tatooine - Larsova farma (Den)\nTicha, vlhka farma rodiny Larsu na Tatooine, obklopena drsnou pousti. Tento skromny domov slouzi jako utociste pro Luka Skywalkera a jeho jednoducha struktura odrazi poustni zivot jeho obyvatel."

REFERENCE           DM_T_LHS
LANG_ENGLISH        "Tatooine - Lars Homestead (Sunset)"
LANG_CZECH       "Tatooine - Larsova farma (Zapad slunce)"

REFERENCE           DM_T_LHS_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Tatooine - Lars Homestead (Sunset)\nThe quiet, moisture farm of the Lars family on Tatooine, surrounded by harsh desert. This humble home serves as a refuge for Luke Skywalker, and its simple structure reflects the desert life of its inhabitants."
LANG_CZECH       "Tatooine - Larsova farma (Zapad slunce)\nTicha, vlhka farma rodiny Larsu na Tatooine, obklopena drsnou pousti. Tento skromny domov slouzi jako utociste pro Luka Skywalkera a jeho jednoducha struktura odrazi poustni zivot jeho obyvatel."

REFERENCE           DM_T_LHN
LANG_ENGLISH        "Tatooine - Lars Homestead (Night)"
LANG_CZECH       "Tatooine - Larsova farma (Noc)"

REFERENCE           DM_T_LHN_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Tatooine - Lars Homestead (Night)\nThe quiet, moisture farm of the Lars family on Tatooine, surrounded by harsh desert. This humble home serves as a refuge for Luke Skywalker, and its simple structure reflects the desert life of its inhabitants."
LANG_CZECH       "Tatooine - Larsova farma (Noc)\nTicha, vlhka farma rodiny Larsu na Tatooine, obklopena drsnou pousti. Tento skromny domov slouzi jako utociste pro Luka Skywalkera a jeho jednoducha struktura odrazi poustni zivot jeho obyvatel."

REFERENCE           DM_SD_TFH
LANG_ENGLISH        "Star Destroyer - TIE Fighter Hangar"
LANG_CZECH       "Hvezdny destruktor - Hangar stihacek TIE"

REFERENCE           DM_SD_TFH_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Star Destroyer - TIE Fighter Hangar\nA hangar aboard an Imperial Star Destroyer, lined with TIE fighters. It serves as the launch point for Imperial starfighters and a hub of military activity."
LANG_CZECH       "Hvezdny Destruktor - Hangar stihacek TIE\nHangar na palube imperialniho hvezdneho destruktoru, lemovany stihackami TIE. Slouzi jako vychozi bod pro imperialni stihacky a centrum vojenskych aktivit."

REFERENCE           DM_K_TC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Kamino - Training Chamber"
LANG_CZECH       "Kamino - Vycvikova mistnost"

REFERENCE           DM_K_TC_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Kamino - Training Chamber\nA high-tech training chamber on Kamino where Starkiller hones his Force abilities. The room is filled with simulations and equipment designed to push a Sith apprentice to his limits."
LANG_CZECH       "Kamino - Vycvikova mistnost\nHigh-tech treninkova komora na Kaminu, kde Starkiller zdokonaluje sve schopnosti Sily. Mistnost je plna simulaci a vybaveni navrzeneho tak, aby posunulo ucednika Sithu na hranici jeho moznosti."

REFERENCE           DM_YV_DA
LANG_ENGLISH        "Yuuzhan Vong - Duel Arena"
LANG_CZECH       "Yuuzhan Vong - Vycvikova arena"

REFERENCE           DM_YV_DA_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Yuuzhan Vong - Duel Arena\nAn ancient combat arena on a Yuuzhan Vong homeworld. Organic architecture and alien carvings surround the battlefield, designed for duels and ritual combat in the Vong tradition."
LANG_CZECH       "Yuuzhan Vong - Vycvikova arena\nStarobyla bojova arena na domovske planete Yuuzhan Vongu. Bojiste obklopuje organicka architektura a mimozemske rezby, ktere jsou urceny pro souboje a ritualni boje podle tradice Vongu."

REFERENCE           DM_DA_EN
LANG_ENGLISH        "Dantooine - Enclave"
LANG_CZECH       "Dantooine - Enklava"

REFERENCE           DM_DA_EN_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Dantooine - Enclave\nA secluded Jedi Enclave on the peaceful world of Dantooine. The grounds serve as a place of study and meditation, where Jedi train in the ways of the Force."
LANG_CZECH       "Dantooine - Enklava\nOdlehla enklava Jediu v poklidnem svete Dantooine. Areal slouzi jako misto studia a meditace, kde se Jediove uci ovladat Silu."

REFERENCE           DM_K_SA
LANG_ENGLISH        "Korriban - Sith Academy"
LANG_CZECH       "Korriban - Akademie Sithu"

REFERENCE           DM_K_SA_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Korriban - Sith Academy\nThe dark training grounds of the Sith on Korriban. Aspirants are taught the ways of the Dark Side amid ancient tombs and foreboding architecture."
LANG_CZECH       "Korriban - Akademie Sithu\nTemne vycvikove tabory Sithu na Korribanu. Aspiranti se uci zpusobum Temne strany uprostred starobylych hrobek a zlovestne architektury."

REFERENCE           DM_L_B
LANG_ENGLISH        "Leviathan - Bridge"
LANG_CZECH       "Leviathan - Mustek"

REFERENCE           DM_L_B_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Leviathan - Bridge\nThe central bridge of the Leviathan starship. Sleek and functional, it serves as the command hub where critical operations are coordinated."
LANG_CZECH       "Leviathan - Mustek\nCentralni mustek vesmirne lodi Leviathan. Elegantni a funkcni, slouzi jako velitelske centrum, kde se koordinuji kriticke operace."

REFERENCE           DM_M_TA
LANG_ENGLISH        "Malachor - Trayus Academy"
LANG_CZECH       "Malachor - Akademie Trayus"

REFERENCE           DM_M_TA_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Malachor - Trayus Academy\nA dark and foreboding academy on Malachor. Here, Sith teachings and experiments push the limits of the Force in a place steeped in shadow."
LANG_CZECH       "Malachor - Akademie Trayus\nTemna a zlovestna akademie na Malachoru. Zde, v miste zahalenem stiny, posouvaji uceni a experimenty Sithu hranice Sily."

REFERENCE           DM_M_TC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Malachor - Trayus Core"
LANG_CZECH       "Malachor - Jadro Akademie Trayus"

REFERENCE           DM_M_TC_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Malachor - Trayus Core\nThe heart of the Trayus Academy, a massive chamber filled with dark energy and remnants of ancient Sith rituals. A place of immense power and danger."
LANG_CZECH       "Malachor - Jadro akademie Trayus\nSrdce Akademie Trayus, obrovska komnata naplnena temnou energii a pozustatky starodavnych ritualu Sithu. Misto nesmirne moci a nebezpeci."

REFERENCE           DM_I_OP
LANG_ENGLISH        "Iziz - Onderon Palace"
LANG_CZECH       "Iziz - Palac na Onderonu"

REFERENCE           DM_I_OP_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Iziz - Onderon Palace\nThe Royal Palace of Iziz was the home of the Royal Family of Onderon throughout the city's history, serving many regimes as the city changed hands over the millennia."
LANG_CZECH       "Iziz - Palac na Onderonu\nKralovsky palac v Izizu byl po celou dobu existence mesta sidlem kralovske rodiny Onderonu a slouzil mnoha rezimum, ktere se v prubehu tisicileti stridaly u moci."

REFERENCE           DM_P_OD
LANG_ENGLISH        "Peragus - Observation Deck"
LANG_CZECH       "Peragus - Pozorovatelna"

REFERENCE           DM_P_OD_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Peragus - Observation Deck\nA vantage point aboard the Peragus mining facility. The observation deck overlooks the station's machinery and corridors, where security droids like HK-50 maintain strict control over the complex."
LANG_CZECH       "Peragus - Pozorovatelna\nVyhlidkove misto na palube tezebniho zarizeni Peragus. Z vyhlidkove plosiny je vyhled na stroje a chodby stanice, kde bezpecnostni droidi jako HK-50 udrzuji prisnou kontrolu nad komplexem."

REFERENCE           DM_R_OD
LANG_ENGLISH        "Ravager - Observation Deck"
LANG_CZECH       "Ravager - Pozorovatelna"

REFERENCE           DM_R_OD_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Ravager - Observation Deck\nA Centurion-class battlecruiser once used by the Republic Navy during the Mandalorian Wars. After being crippled by the Mass Shadow Generator, it now serves under Darth Nihilus."
LANG_CZECH       "Ravager - Pozorovatelna\nBitevni kriznik tridy Centurion, ktery kdysi pouzivalo namornictvo Republiky behem Mandalorianskych valek. Pote, co byl poskozen Generatorem masoveho stinu, nyni slouzi pod velenim Dartha Nihiluse."

REFERENCE           DM_T_H
LANG_ENGLISH        "Taris - Horizons"
LANG_CZECH       "Taris - Horizonty"

REFERENCE           DM_T_H_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Taris - Horizons\nThe bustling upper levels of Taris, filled with towers, platforms, and traffic. Horizons showcase the city's scale and the diversity of its inhabitants."
LANG_CZECH       "Taris - Horizonty\nRusne horni urovne Tarisu, plne vezi, plosin a dopravy. Horizonty ukazuji rozlohu mesta a rozmanitost jeho obyvatel."

REFERENCE           DM_T_CS
LANG_ENGLISH        "Telos - Citadel Station"
LANG_CZECH       "Telos - Stanice Citadela"

REFERENCE           DM_T_CS_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Telos - Citadel Station\nThe central hub of Telos, serving as a command and administrative center. Citadel Station oversees the planet's operations and maintains order."
LANG_CZECH       "Telos - Stanice Citadela\nCentralni uzel Telosu, ktery slouzi jako velitelske a administrativni centrum. Stanice Citadela dohlizi na provoz planety a udrzuje poradek."

REFERENCE           DM_T_PA
LANG_ENGLISH        "Telos - Polar Academy"
LANG_CZECH       "Telos - Polarni Akademie"

REFERENCE           DM_T_PA_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Telos - Polar Academy\nA remote training facility located in Telos' polar region. The academy is dedicated to study and discipline, offering harsh conditions to strengthen its trainees."
LANG_CZECH       "Telos - Polarni Akademie\nVzdalene vycvikove stredisko nachazejici se v polarni oblasti Telosu. Akademie se venuje studiu a discipline a nabizi drsne podminky, ktere posiluji jeji studenty."

REFERENCE           DM_R_VOTJ
LANG_ENGLISH        "DF2 - Valley Of The Jedi"
LANG_CZECH       "DF2 - Udoli Jediu"

REFERENCE           DM_R_VOTJ_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "DF2 - Valley Of The Jedi\nThe Valley of the Jedi is a mystical, ancient site on the planet Ruusan, filled with powerful Force energy. It is a place where Jedi and Sith alike are drawn to harness the power of the Force."
LANG_CZECH       "DF2 - Udoli Jediu\nUdoli Jediu je mysticke, starobyle misto na planete Ruusan, naplnene mocnou energii Sily. Je to misto, kam jsou pritahovani jak Jediove, tak Sithove, aby vyuzili moc Sily."

REFERENCE           DM_K_TOR
LANG_ENGLISH        "Korriban - Tomb Of Ragnos"
LANG_CZECH       "Korriban - Ragnosova hrobka"

REFERENCE           DM_K_TOR_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Korriban - Tomb Of Ragnos\nThe Tomb of Ragnos on Korriban is a sacred burial site for the ancient Sith Lords. Its dark, foreboding atmosphere is filled with the remnants of long-dead Sith, with many dark secrets hidden beneath its sands."
LANG_CZECH       "Korriban - Ragnosova hrobka\nHrobka Ragnose na Korribanu je posvatnym pohrebistem Sithskych Lordu. Jeji temna, zlovestna atmosfera je naplnena pozustatky davno zemrelych Sithu a pod jejim piskem se skryva mnoho temnych tajemstvi."

REFERENCE           DM_D1_BC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Duel1 - Bespin Courtyard"
LANG_CZECH       "Duel1 - Nadvori na Bespinu"

REFERENCE           DM_D1_BC_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Duel1 - Bespin Courtyard\nA grand courtyard set on the floating city of Bespin, this location serves as the stage for intense duels."
LANG_CZECH       "Duel1 - Nadvori na Bespinu\nVelkolepe nadvori ve vznasejicim se meste Bespin slouzi jako dejiste napinavych souboju."

REFERENCE           DM_D3_IS
LANG_ENGLISH        "Duel3 - Imperial Shaft"
LANG_CZECH       "Duel3 - Imperialni sachta"

REFERENCE           DM_D3_IS_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Duel3 - Imperial Shaft\nA dark, industrial shaft deep within an Imperial facility. Its narrow, vertical design makes it an ideal setting for intense, close-quarters duels, with little room for escape."
LANG_CZECH       "Duel3 - Imperialni sachta\nTemna prumyslova sachta hluboko v imperialnim zarizeni. Diky svemu uzkemu vertikalnimu usporadani je idealnim mistem pro intenzivni souboje na kratkou vzdalenost, kde neni temer zadny prostor pro unik."

REFERENCE           DM_D4_ICR
LANG_ENGLISH        "Duel4 - Imperial Control Room"
LANG_CZECH       "Duel4 - Imperialni ridici mistnost"

REFERENCE           DM_D4_ICR_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Duel4 - Imperial Control Room\nA high-tech, command center aboard an Imperial ship. The Imperial Control Room is the nerve center of operations, with its vast displays and futuristic equipment creating a tense atmosphere for combat."
LANG_CZECH       "Duel4 - Imperialni ridici mistnost\nHigh-tech velitelske centrum na palube imperialni lodi. Imperialni velitelska mistnost je nervovym centrem operaci, kde obrovske displeje a futuristicke vybaveni vytvareji napjatou atmosferu pro boj."

REFERENCE           DM_D5_TL
LANG_ENGLISH        "Duel5 - Taspir Landing"
LANG_CZECH       "Duel5 - Pristavaci plosina na Taspiru"

REFERENCE           DM_D5_TL_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Duel5 - Taspir Landing\nA desolate, barren landing site on the planet Taspir, surrounded by rocky terrain and lava. The open space and hostile environment make it a challenging location for combatants."
LANG_CZECH       "Duel5 - Pristavaci plosina na Taspiru\nPuste, neurodne misto ke pristani na planete Taspir, obklopene skalnatym terenem a lavou. Otevreny prostor a nepratelske prostredi z nej cini narocne misto pro bojujici strany."

REFERENCE           DM_D6_YTG
LANG_ENGLISH        "Duel6 - Yavin Training Grounds"
LANG_CZECH       "Duel6 - Treninkovy areal na Yavinu"

REFERENCE           DM_D6_YTG_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Duel6 - Yavin Training Grounds\nThe Yavin Training Grounds are an expansive, open-air area filled with training droids and obstacles. It is the perfect place for honing combat skills in a more controlled environment."
LANG_CZECH       "Duel6 - Treninkovy areal na Yavinu\nTreninkovy areal na Yavinu je rozlehla venkovni plocha plna vycvikovych droidu a prekazek. Je to idealni misto pro zdokonalovani bojovych dovednosti v kontrolovanejsim prostredi."

REFERENCE           DM_D7_RP
LANG_ENGLISH        "Duel7 - Rancor Pit"
LANG_CZECH       "Duel7 - Rancorovo doupe"

REFERENCE           DM_D7_RP_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Duel7 - Rancor Pit\nA dark, ominous pit used for the display of the feared Rancor, a deadly creature. The pit is a location for combatants to fight, with the threat of the Rancor looming over the duels."
LANG_CZECH       "Duel7 - Rancorovo doupe\nTemna, zlovestna jama slouzici k vystavovani obavaneho Rancora, smrticiho tvora. Jama je mistem, kde bojovnici svadeji souboje, pricemz nad duely visi hrozba Rancora."

REFERENCE           DM_D8_AC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Duel8 - Abandoned City"
LANG_CZECH       "Duel8 - Opustene mesto"

REFERENCE           DM_D8_AC_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Duel8 - Abandoned City\nAn eerie, forgotten city filled with crumbling buildings and deserted streets. The abandoned city offers a dangerous environment where duelists must navigate the ruins as they face off against each other."
LANG_CZECH       "Duel8 - Opustene mesto\nStrasidelne, zapomenute mesto plne rozpadajicich se budov a opustenych ulic. Opustene mesto nabizi nebezpecne prostredi, kde se duelanti musi pohybovat mezi ruinami, zatimco proti sobe bojuji."

REFERENCE           DM_D10_VFP
LANG_ENGLISH        "Duel10 - Vjun Fuel Processing"
LANG_CZECH       "Duel10 - Zpracovani paliva na Vjunu"

REFERENCE           DM_D10_VFP_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Duel10 - Vjun Fuel Processing\nA harsh, industrial facility on the planet Vjun. The fuel processing plant is filled with machinery and dark, toxic environments, providing a grim backdrop for fierce duels."
LANG_CZECH       "Duel10 - Zpracovani paliva na Vjunu\nDrsne prumyslove zarizeni na planete Vjun. Zavod na zpracovani paliva je plny stroju a temneho, toxickeho prostredi, ktere poskytuje ponure kulisy pro zurive souboje."

REFERENCE           DM_CTF1_IDZ
LANG_ENGLISH        "CTF1 - Imperial Drop Zone"
LANG_CZECH       "CTF1 - Imperialni vysadkova zona"

REFERENCE           DM_CTF1_IDZ_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "CTF1 - Imperial Drop Zone\nA fortified Imperial drop zone, where heavy military activity takes place. The area is littered with corridors and advantage points offering tactical advantages for both teams in capture the flag matches."
LANG_CZECH       "CTF1 - Imperialni vysadkova zona\nOpevnena imperialni vysadkova zona, kde probiha intenzivni vojenska cinnost. Oblast je poseta chodbami a vyhodnymi body, ktere nabizeji takticke vyhody pro oba tymy v zapasech o dobyti vlajky."

REFERENCE           DM_CF2_HW
LANG_ENGLISH        "CTF2 - Hoth Wasteland"
LANG_CZECH       "CTF2 - Pustina na Hothu"

REFERENCE           DM_CF2_HW_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "CTF2 - Hoth Wasteland\nA frozen, desolate wasteland on the icy planet of Hoth, covered in snowdrifts and ice. The harsh environment makes movement difficult, but offers plenty of opportunities for tactical positioning in capture the flag."
LANG_CZECH       "CTF2 - Pustina na Hothu\nZmrzla, pusta pustina na ledove planete Hoth, pokryta snehovymi zavejemi a ledem. Drsne prostredi ztezuje pohyb, ale nabizi spoustu prilezitosti pro takticke rozmisteni pri hre ziskej vlajku."

REFERENCE           DM_CF3_YH
LANG_ENGLISH        "CTF3 - Yavin Hilltops"
LANG_CZECH       "CTF3 - Vrcholy kopcu na Yavinu"

REFERENCE           DM_CF3_YH_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "CTF3 - Yavin Hilltops\nThe hilltops of Yavin IV, overlooking the jungle-covered landscape. This elevated position offers wide-ranging views and strategic vantage points for capture the flag gameplay."
LANG_CZECH       "CTF3 - Vrcholy kopcu na Yavinu\nVrcholky kopcu Yavin IV, tycici se nad dzungli pokrytou krajinou. Tato vyvysena poloha nabizi siroky vyhled a strategicke vyhodne pozice pro hru typu ziskej vlajku."

REFERENCE           DM_CF4_CS
LANG_ENGLISH        "CTF4 - Coruscant Streets"
LANG_CZECH       "CTF4 - Ulice Coruscantu"

REFERENCE           DM_CF4_CS_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "CTF4 - Coruscant Streets\nThe bustling, urban streets of Coruscant provide an exciting and dynamic environment for capture the flag. The densely packed cityscape offers plenty of cover and opportunities for ambushes."
LANG_CZECH       "CTF4 - Ulice Coruscantu\nRusne mestske ulice Coruscantu poskytuji vzrusujici a dynamicke prostredi pro hru ziskej vlajku. Huste zastavena mestska krajina nabizi spoustu ukrytu a prilezitosti k prepadeni."

REFERENCE           DM_CF5_F
LANG_ENGLISH        "CTF5 - Factory"
LANG_CZECH       "CTF5 - Tovarna"

REFERENCE           DM_CF5_F_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "CTF5 - Factory\nA large, industrial factory filled with towering machines and narrow catwalks. The factory's complex layout creates both obstacles and advantages for teams in capture the flag matches."
LANG_CZECH       "CTF5 - Tovarna\nVelka prumyslova tovarna plna vysokych stroju a uzkych lavek. Slozita dispozice tovarny predstavuje pro tymy v zapasech typu ziskej vlajku jak prekazky, tak vyhody."

REFERENCE           DM_FFA1_VS
LANG_ENGLISH        "FFA1 - Vjun Sentinel"
LANG_CZECH       "FFA1 - Straz na Vjunu"

REFERENCE           DM_FFA1_VS_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "FFA1 - Vjun Sentinel\nA dark, stormy world with a gothic atmosphere, Vjun Sentinel features towering structures and a foreboding landscape. The terrain offers dangerous drops and narrow platforms for intense free-for-all combat."
LANG_CZECH       "FFA1 - Straz na Vjunu\nVjun je temny, bourlivy svet s gotickou atmosferou, ktery se vyznacuje vysokymi stavbami a zlovestnou krajinou. Teren nabizi nebezpecne srazky a uzke plosiny pro intenzivni boje vsech proti vsem."

REFERENCE           DM_FFA2_K
LANG_ENGLISH        "FFA2 - Korriban"
LANG_CZECH       "#same"

REFERENCE           DM_FFA2_K_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "FFA2 - Korriban\nThe ancient, desert world of Korriban, home to the tombs of Sith Lords. Its eerie, tomb-laden landscape creates a haunting setting for intense, chaotic battles between combatants."
LANG_CZECH       "FFA2 - Korriban\nStarobyly poustni svet Korriban, domov hrobek Sithskych Lordu. Jeho desiva krajina plna hrobek vytvari strasidelnou kulisu pro intenzivni a chaoticke bitvy mezi bojovniky."

REFERENCE           DM_FFA3_T
LANG_ENGLISH        "FFA3 - Tatooine"
LANG_CZECH       "#same"

REFERENCE           DM_FFA3_T_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "FFA3 - Tatooine\nThe harsh desert planet of Tatooine, with vast open spaces, rocky terrain, and sparse settlements. This location offers both wide views and tight, perilous corners perfect for free-for-all confrontations."
LANG_CZECH       "FFA3 - Tatooine\nDrsna poustni planeta Tatooine s rozlehlymi otevrenymi prostranstvimi, skalnatym terenem a ridkymi osadami. Tato lokace nabizi jak siroke vyhledy, tak uzke, nebezpecne zakouti, ktere jsou idealni pro souboje vsech proti vsem."

REFERENCE           DM_FFA4_RS
LANG_ENGLISH        "FFA4 - Rift Sanctuary"
LANG_CZECH       "FFA4 - Svatyne na Riftu"

REFERENCE           DM_FFA4_RS_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "FFA4 - Rift Sanctuary\nA mysterious, secluded sanctuary surrounded by dangerous rifts in the landscape. Its crumbling architecture and hazardous environment make for a volatile battleground where danger lurks at every turn."
LANG_CZECH       "FFA4 - Svatyne na Riftu\nTajemne, odlehle utociste obklopene nebezpecnymi trhlinami v krajine. Jeho rozpadajici se architektura a nebezpecne prostredi z nej cini nestabilni bojiste, kde na kazdem kroku ciha nebezpeci."

REFERENCE           DM_FFA5_T
LANG_ENGLISH        "FFA5 - Taspir"
LANG_CZECH       "#same"

REFERENCE           DM_FFA5_T_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "FFA5 - Taspir\nA desolate, rocky planet with harsh terrain and minimal shelter. Taspir's rugged environment forces players to rely on quick reflexes and strategic positioning in free-for-all battles."
LANG_CZECH       "FFA5 - Taspir\nPusta, skalnata planeta s drsnym terenem a minimem ukrytu. Drsne prostredi Taspiru nuti hrace spolehat se na rychle reflexy a strategicke umisteni v bitvach, kde kazdy bojuje sam za sebe."

REFERENCE           DM_SIEGE_DR
LANG_ENGLISH        "Siege - Desert Rescue"
LANG_CZECH       "Siege - Zachrana v pousti"

REFERENCE           DM_SIEGE_DR_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Siege - Desert Rescue\nA barren desert planet, where an intense rescue mission is underway. The vast, sandy landscape provides few places to hide, creating a tense atmosphere for both defenders and attackers in siege-style combat."
LANG_CZECH       "Siege - Zachrana v pousti\nNeurodna poustni planeta, kde probiha intenzivni zachranna mise. Rozlehla piscita krajina nabizi jen malo mist, kde se lze schovat, coz vytvari napjatou atmosferu jak pro obrance, tak pro utocniky v boji typu oblehani."

REFERENCE           DM_SIEGE_K
LANG_ENGLISH        "Siege - Korriban"
LANG_CZECH       "#same"

REFERENCE           DM_SIEGE_K_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Siege - Korriban\nA powerful, ancient Sith world, Korriban's dark temples and tombs set the stage for brutal siege warfare. The harsh desert terrain and tight corridors make it a perfect location for high-stakes battles."
LANG_CZECH       "Siege - Korriban\nKorriban, mocny starobyly svet Sithu, se svymi temnymi chramy a hrobkami je dejistem brutalnich oblehacich valek. Drsny poustni teren a uzke chodby z nej cini idealni misto pro bitvy s vysokymi sazkami."

REFERENCE           DM_SF_OD
LANG_ENGLISH        "Star Forge - Observation Deck"
LANG_CZECH       "Star Forge - Pozorovatelna"

REFERENCE           DM_SF_OD_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Star Forge - Observation Deck\nA sleek, metallic observation deck aboard the Star Forge. The cold, industrial design offers little cover but provides wide views of the Forge's inner workings, making for a tense battleground."
LANG_CZECH       "Star Forge - Pozorovatelna\nElegantni kovova vyhlidkova plosina na palube Star Forge. Chladny industrialni design nabizi jen malo ukrytu, ale poskytuje siroky vyhled na vnitrni fungovani Forge, coz z nej cini napinave bojiste."

REFERENCE           DM_DF2_SC
LANG_ENGLISH        "MOTS - Sith Catacombs"
LANG_CZECH       "MOTS - Sithske katakomby"

REFERENCE           DM_DF2_SC_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "MOTS - Sith Catacombs\nDeep beneath the Sith stronghold, the Sith Catacombs are filled with dark passages and ancient traps. The eerie, tomb-like atmosphere makes it a treacherous environment for any combatant."
LANG_CZECH       "MOTS - Sithske katakomby\nHluboko pod pevnosti Sithu se nachazeji katakomby Sithu, ktere jsou plne temnych chodeb a starodavnych pasti. Strasidelna atmosfera pripominajici hrobku z nich cini zradne prostredi pro kazdeho bojovnika."

REFERENCE           DM_DF2_TV
LANG_ENGLISH        "DF2 - The Vengeance"
LANG_CZECH       "#same"

REFERENCE           DM_DF2_TV_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "DF2 - The Vengeance\nA slender, black KDY Super Star Destroyer that served as the flagship of the Dark Jedi Jerec in the years before and after the Battle of Endor. It was commanded by Captain Sysco."
LANG_CZECH       "DF2 - The Vengeance\nStihla cerna lod KDY Super Hvezdny Destruktor, ktera slouzila jako vlajkova lod temneho Jediho Jereca v letech pred a po Bitve o Endor. Velel ji kapitan Sysco."

REFERENCE           DM_DF2_DP
LANG_ENGLISH        "DF2 - Dark Palace"
LANG_CZECH       "DF2 - Temny palac"

REFERENCE           DM_DF2_DP_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "DF2 - Dark Palace\nA lavish yet sinister palace filled with dark energy. The towering spires and ornate chambers of the Dark Palace offer both beauty and danger, with traps and ambush points around every corner."
LANG_CZECH       "DF2 - Temny palac\nNadherny, ale zlovestny palac naplneny temnou energii. Vysoke veze a zdobene komnaty Temneho palace nabizeji jak krasu, tak nebezpeci, s pastmi a ukryty na kazdem rohu."

REFERENCE           DM_DF2_SS
LANG_ENGLISH        "DF2 - Sulon Star"
LANG_CZECH       "#same"

REFERENCE           DM_DF2_SS_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "DF2 - Sulon Star\nA massive, derelict freighter drifting in space. The dark, industrial corridors provide a perfect backdrop for the deadly confrontation with the Dark Jedi, Pic and Gorc, in this claustrophobic, high-stakes battle."
LANG_CZECH       "DF2 - Sulon Star\nObrovska, opustena nakladni lod plujici vesmirem. Temne, industrialni chodby poskytuji dokonalou kulisu pro smrtici konfrontaci s temnymi Jedi, Picem a Gorcem, v teto klaustrofobicke bitve s vysokymi sazkami."

REFERENCE           DM_DF2_JB
LANG_ENGLISH        "DF2 - Jedi Battleground"
LANG_CZECH       "DF2 - Bitevni pole Jediu"

REFERENCE           DM_DF2_JB_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "DF2 - Jedi Battleground\nA desolate, ruined landscape where the wreckage of a crashed ship lies amidst ancient ruins. The location marks the final confrontation between Kyle and Sarris, after the defeat of Maw, in a chaotic and explosive battle."
LANG_CZECH       "DF2 - Bitevni pole Jediu\nPusta, znicene krajina, kde trosky havarovane lodi lezi uprostred starobylych ruin. Toto misto je dejistem finalniho stretu mezi Kylem a Sarris po porazce Mawa v chaoticke a dramaticke bitve."

REFERENCE           DM_DF2_R
LANG_ENGLISH        "DF2 - Tower"
LANG_CZECH       "DF2 - Vez"

REFERENCE           DM_DF2_R_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "DF2 - Tower\nAn imposing, dark tower, where Kyle must confront the twisted Dark Jedi, Maw. The high-altitude battleground features narrow ledges and a sense of vertigo, adding to the intensity of the final fight."
LANG_CZECH       "DF2 - Vez\nImpozantni temna vez, kde Kyle musi celit zvracenemu temnemu Jediovi Mawovi. Bojiste ve vysoke nadmorske vysce se vyznacuje uzkymi rimsami a pocitem zavrate, coz jeste umocnuje intenzitu finalniho souboje."

REFERENCE           DM_JKO_D_BA
LANG_ENGLISH        "Duel1 - Bay"
LANG_CZECH       "Duel1 - Hangar"

REFERENCE           DM_JKO_D_BA_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Duel1 - Bay (Requires Jedi Outcast)\nA spacious, industrial bay filled for ships. The open space offers plenty of room for combatants to maneuver, but also presents risks with the environment's hazards."
LANG_CZECH       "Duel1 - Hangar (Vyzaduje Jedi Outcast)\nProstorna prumyslova hala pro lode. Otevreny prostor nabizi bojovnikum dostatek mista k manevrovani, ale take predstavuje rizika spojena s nebezpecim prostredi."

REFERENCE           DM_JKO_D_BE
LANG_ENGLISH        "Duel2 - Bespin"
LANG_CZECH       "#same"

REFERENCE           DM_JKO_D_BE_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Duel2 - Bespin (Requires Jedi Outcast)\nSet in the floating city of Bespin. The environment provides small platforms for intense dueling."
LANG_CZECH       "Duel2 - Bespin (Vyzaduje Jedi Outcast)\nDej se odehrava ve vznasejicim se meste Bespin. Prostredi nabizi male plosiny pro intenzivni souboje."

REFERENCE           DM_JKO_D_HA
LANG_ENGLISH        "Duel3 - Hangar"
LANG_CZECH       "#same"

REFERENCE           DM_JKO_D_HA_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Duel3 - Hangar (Requires Jedi Outcast)\nA large hangar bay filled with cargo, and industrial equipment. The cluttered environment provides plenty of cover for stealthy maneuvers, but also creates dangerous obstacles for combatants."
LANG_CZECH       "Duel3 - Hangar (Vyzaduje Jedi Outcast)\nVelky hangar plny nakladu a prumysloveho vybaveni. Neporadek v prostredi poskytuje dostatek ukrytu pro tajne manevry, ale take vytvari nebezpecne prekazky pro bojujici strany."

REFERENCE           DM_JKO_D_PI
LANG_ENGLISH        "Duel4 - Pit"
LANG_CZECH       "Duel4 - Jama"

REFERENCE           DM_JKO_D_PI_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "Duel4 - Pit (Requires Jedi Outcast)\nA dark, ominous pit surrounded by platforms and steep drops. This confined space forces duelists into close-quarters combat, with little room for escape or evasion."
LANG_CZECH       "Duel4 - Jama (Vyzaduje Jedi Outcast)\nTemna, zlovestna jama obklopena plosinami a strmymi stenami. Tento stisneny prostor nuti duelanty k boji zblizka, pri kterem je jen malo prostoru pro unik nebo uhyb."

REFERENCE           DM_JKO_F_BE
LANG_ENGLISH        "FFA1 - Bespin"
LANG_CZECH       "#same"

REFERENCE           DM_JKO_F_BE_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "FFA1 - Bespin (Requires Jedi Outcast)\nA bustling environment in Bespin's floating city, with a mix of open air platforms and narrow passageways. The city's futuristic architecture provides plenty of opportunities for both long-range and close-quarters combat."
LANG_CZECH       "FFA1 - Bespin (Vyzaduje Jedi Outcast)\nRusne prostredi ve vznasejicim se meste Bespin, kde se misi otevrene plosiny a uzke chodby. Futuristicka architektura mesta nabizi spoustu prilezitosti pro boj na dlouhou i kratkou vzdalenost."

REFERENCE           DM_JKO_F_DE
LANG_ENGLISH        "FFA2 - Death Star"
LANG_CZECH       "FFA2 - Hvezda Smrti"

REFERENCE           DM_JKO_F_DE_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "FFA2 - Death Star (Requires Jedi Outcast)\nThe Emperor's Throne Room with tight spaces and cold, metallic design create a hostile environment for free-for-all battles."
LANG_CZECH       "FFA2 - Hvezda Smrti (Vyzaduje Jedi Outcast)\nCisarsky trunni sal s omezenym prostorem a chladnym, kovovym designem vytvari nepratelske prostredi pro bitvy vsech proti vsem."

REFERENCE           DM_JKO_F_IM
LANG_ENGLISH        "FFA3 - Imperial"
LANG_CZECH       "FFA3 - Imperialni destruktor"

REFERENCE           DM_JKO_F_IM_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "FFA3 - Imperial (Requires Jedi Outcast)\nA cold, stark environment within an Imperial star destroyer. The sterile, industrial design offers little cover, making it a high-risk arena for combatants looking for quick and decisive engagements."
LANG_CZECH       "FFA3 - Imperialni destruktor (Vyzaduje Jedi Outcast)\nChladne, strohe prostredi uvnitr Imperialniho hvezdneho destruktoru. Sterilni, industrialni design nabizi jen malo ukrytu, coz z nej cini vysoce rizikovou arenu pro bojovniky, kteri hledaji rychle a rozhodujici strety."

REFERENCE           DM_JKO_F_NH
LANG_ENGLISH        "FFA4 - Hideout"
LANG_CZECH       "FFA4 - Ukryt"

REFERENCE           DM_JKO_F_NH_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "FFA4 - Hideout (Requires Jedi Outcast)\nA hidden, underground hideout filled with narrow corridors and cluttered rooms. The environment's tight spaces force players to be quick and stealthy, using the surroundings to their advantage."
LANG_CZECH       "FFA4 - Ukryt (Vyzaduje Jedi Outcast)\nSkryty podzemni ukryt plny uzkych chodeb a preplnenych mistnosti. Stisnene prostory nuti hrace byt rychli a nenapadni a vyuzivat okoli ve svuj prospech."

REFERENCE           DM_JKO_F_NS
LANG_ENGLISH        "FFA5 - Streets"
LANG_CZECH       "FFA5 - Ulice"

REFERENCE           DM_JKO_F_NS_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "FFA5 - Streets (Requires Jedi Outcast)\nA dense, urban environment filled with narrow alleys and open streets. The cityscape offers plenty of places for ambushes and surprise attacks, making it a chaotic setting for free-for-all battles."
LANG_CZECH       "FFA5 - Ulice (Vyzaduje Jedi Outcast)\nHuste mestske prostredi plne uzkych ulicek a otevrenych ulic. Mestska krajina nabizi spoustu mist pro prepady a prekvapive utoky, coz z ni cini chaoticke prostredi pro bitvy vsech proti vsem."

REFERENCE           DM_JKO_F_RA
LANG_ENGLISH        "FFA6 - Raven"
LANG_CZECH       "#same"

REFERENCE           DM_JKO_F_RA_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "FFA6 - Raven (Requires Jedi Outcast)\nA dark, mysterious environment set in a crumbling, ancient structure. The ruinous design offers plenty of shadows and verticality, with hazards lurking at every corner for those brave enough to fight here."
LANG_CZECH       "FFA6 - Raven (Vyzaduje Jedi Outcast)\nTemne, tajemne prostredi zasazene do rozpadajici se starobyle stavby. Zchatraly design nabizi spoustu stinu a vertikality, pricemz na kazdeho, kdo se odvazi zde bojovat, cihaji na kazdem rohu nebezpeci."

REFERENCE           DM_JKO_F_YA
LANG_ENGLISH        "FFA7 - Yavin"
LANG_CZECH       "#same"

REFERENCE           DM_JKO_F_YA_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "FFA7 - Yavin (Requires Jedi Outcast)\nThe ancient temple provides the perfect arena for chaotic close-quarters combat in free-for-all battles."
LANG_CZECH       "FFA7 - Yavin (Vyzaduje Jedi Outcast)\nStarobyly chram poskytuje idealni arenu pro chaoticke boje zblizka v bitvach vsech proti vsem."

REFERENCE           DM_JKO_C_IM
LANG_ENGLISH        "CTF1 - Imperial"
LANG_CZECH       "CTF1 - Imperialni zakladna"

REFERENCE           DM_JKO_C_IM_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "CTF1 - Imperial (Requires Jedi Outcast)\nA fortress-like Imperial base, with well-defended corridors and strategic points for capture the flag matches. The imposing structure offers both tactical advantages and risks for players seeking control."
LANG_CZECH       "CTF1 - Imperialni zakladna (Vyzaduje Jedi Outcast)\nPevnostni Imperialni zakladna s dobre branenymi chodbami a strategickymi body pro zapasy typu ziskej vlajku. Impozantni stavba nabizi takticke vyhody i rizika pro hrace, kteri se snazi ziskat kontrolu."

REFERENCE           DM_JKO_C_YA
LANG_ENGLISH        "CTF2 - Yavin"
LANG_CZECH       "#same"

REFERENCE           DM_JKO_C_YA_DESC
LANG_ENGLISH        "CTF2 - Yavin (Requires Jedi Outcast)\nThe ancient ruins provide a mix of open spaces and tight, hidden spots for capture the flag gameplay. The environment rewards stealth and strategy."
LANG_CZECH       "CTF2 - Yavin (Vyzaduje Jedi Outcast)\nStarobyle ruiny poskytuji kombinaci otevrenych prostoru a uzkych, skrytych mist pro hru typu ziskej vlajku. Prostredi odmenuje nenapadnost a strategii."

