REFERENCE           TOTG_WELCOME
LANG_ENGLISH        "Welcome to Movie Duels: Tales of the Galaxy! \n\n Join us and relive legendary stories across the Star Wars universe. Replay the duels from Dark Forces 2 as Kyle Katarn against Jerec and the dark Jedi Knights in Season 1 of Tales of the Galaxy! Other seasons will become available in future updates!"
LANG_CZECH       "Vitejte v Movie Duels: Pribehy z Galaxie! \n\n Pridejte se k nam a prozijte legendarni pribehy napric vesmirem Hvezdnych valek. V sezone 1 si zahrajte souboje ze hry Dark Forces 2 jako Kyle Katarn proti Jerecovi a jeho Temnym Jedium! Dalsi sezony budou k dispozici v budoucich aktualizacich!"

REFERENCE           TOTG_KELDOR_WELCOME
LANG_ENGLISH        "Welcome to the Galaxy Map of Movie Duels: Tales of the Galaxy! \n\n Select and relive a story from the map to get started. Have fun and may the Force be with you!"
LANG_CZECH       "Vitejte v galakticke mape Movie Duels: Pribehy z Galaxie! \n\n Na mape si zvolte pribeh a prozijte ho. Bavte se a kez je Sila s Vami!"

